    "en": {
      "title": "Lanka IOC Notification issued by the company",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Lanka IOC Lanka I.O.C said that the fuel distribution will take place as usual at the fuel stations from today. The company announced.",
        "As well as the Lanka IOC located in Trincomalee. The company has announced that the company-owned fuel depot will operate 24 hours a day. (a)"
      ],
